mework communities, WordPress seems to be a little behind in creating a fast and efficient roll out process. The whole thing seems a little “work it out yourself”. &nbsp; That being said, there are hundreds of tools [&hellip;]</p>\n","featured_media":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.829268292682927,"src":"/static/6536f16ccc86bdec9cbd30263ed32848/db7af/bedrock-trellis-1.jpg","srcSet":"/static/6536f16ccc86bdec9cbd30263ed32848/8f9a6/bedrock-trellis-1.jpg 250w,\n/static/6536f16ccc86bdec9cbd30263ed32848/6a7a1/bedrock-trellis-1.jpg 500w,\n/static/6536f16ccc86bdec9cbd30263ed32848/db7af/bedrock-trellis-1.jpg 750w","sizes":"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px"}}},"title":"Bedrock &#038; Trellis","alt_text":"Bedrock & Trellis WordPress Development"},"categories":[{"name":"Coding"},{"name":"General Coding"},{"name":"Inspiration"},{"name":"Ramblings"},{"name":"WordPress"}],"tags":[{"name":"Bedrock"},{"name":"Framework"},{"name":"Inspiration"},{"name":"Roots"},{"name":"Snippets"},{"name":"Teaching"},{"name":"Training"},{"name":"Trellis"},{"name":"Vagrant"},{"name":"VirtualMachine"},{"name":"WordPress"}]}},{"node":{"id":"6add6f42-2cfd-53e4-bc1d-466b0ade31bb","slug":"first-taste-of-grav","template":"","format":"standard","title":"First Taste of Grav","date":"2018-10-29, 11:00:46","modified":"2018-10-28, 16:46:47","excerpt":"<p>Up until recently I have been predominantly a WordPress based developer. I have dabbled in other things, a little bit of React here and there but nothing crazy. Recently however, I have felt a bit nonplussed with it all. Everything seems to take a little bit too long to spin up, and although I have [&hellip;]</p>\n","featured_media":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.829268292682927,"src":"/static/df3af16008f59f9b2d02358c16365583/db7af/grav-1.jpg","srcSet":"/static/df3af16008f59f9b2d02358c16365583/8f9a6/grav-1.jpg 250w,\n/static/df3af16008f59f9b2